## Protocol.SystemInfo.GetInfoResponse.modelName property

A platform-dependent description of the model of the machine. On Mac OS, this is, for example, 'MacBookPro'. Will be the empty string if not supported.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
modelName: string;
```
